cetus.hir

Class StandardLibrary

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.hir.StandardLibrary

  • public class StandardLibrary
extends java.lang.Object
    Repository for C99 standard library functions. This class provides a basic information about the standard library calls. Knowing that if a function call may or must not have side effects can greatly improve the precision of a program analysis in general. Standard library calls may have side effects on the parameters, on the automatic storage locations, on the file system, and on the execution environment.
